rComments: Very good professor! She might not be as knowledgeable as some other profs I've had, but she is very good at encouraging critical analysis and looking at things through different lenses. Assignments are interesting, lectures and tests are clear, and she is a good lecturer. She is also very nice if you can chat with her outside of class. Easy A IMO.
Her lectures were so good. She kept it really interesting. She used lots of media too which was fun. Truly recommend her as a prof.

Best prof I've had in my 4 years at university. Uses a wide variety of media, shows movie clips, news headlines, music clips. Fun stories. Knows all of her students by name. Writes many comments on papers. Lots of reading required for the course... but well worth it!
